\c 24
\s Simudzai misoro yenyu, masuo!
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Nyika ndeyaJehovha, nokuzara kwayo; Nyika yose navageremo.
\v 2 Nokuti wakaiteya pamusoro pamakungwa, Nokuisimbisa pamusoro penzizi.
\p
\v 3 Ndiani angakwira mugomo raJehovha?
\s Ndiani ungamira panzvimbo yake tsvene?
\p
\v 4 Uyo anamaoko akachena,
\s nomwoyo wakanaka kwazvo; Asingasimudziri mwoyo wake kune zvisina maturo,
\s Neasina kupika nhema.
\p
\v 5 Iye achapiwa mukomborero naJehovha,
\s Nokururamiswa naMwari muponesi wake.
\p
\v 6 Urwu ndirwo rudzi rwavanomutsvaka,
\s Vanotsvaka chiso chenyu, imi Mwari waJakobho.
\s Simudzai misoro yenyu, imi masuo; Musimudzwe imi, magonhi akare-kare;
\s Kuti Mambo wokubwinya apinde.
\p
\v 8 Ndianiko iye Mambo wokubwinya? Ndiye Jehovha ane simba
\s noumhare,
\s Iye Jehovha anoumhare pakurwa.
\p
\v 9 Simudzai misoro yenyu, imi masuo; Muisimudze, imi magonhi akare-kare;
\s Kuti Mambo wokubwinya apinde.
\p
\v 10 Ndianiko uyu Mambo wokubwinya? Jehovha wehondo,
\s Ndiye Mambo wokubwinya.
